      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on pedicle screw geometry. Von Mises stress and reaction force QoIs converged to within 1.1% between medium and fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation GCI < 0.8%. Final mesh selected at medium density balancing accuracy and runtime. Achieved level meets required level."
